ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba78fc1c2262add5251301f7648d70f3b80a1a16","tid":163723,"uid":67119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"仲係呢埋左邊影到相喎，但係係梳化底好大塵同污糟怕唔怕有問題？"},{"pid":"f11e80b2d2149494dcac1cea20a482413c8645a3","tid":163723,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"放隻自動識走既野，細細隻，佢會撲出黎捉<br />\n或者雷射筆紅色一點射落sofa對出地面"},{"pid":"ee04b377868833ec8d2ed6a66572c1d655b659c6","tid":163723,"uid":67119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放隻自動識走既野，細細隻，佢會撲出黎捉<br />\n或者雷射筆紅色一點射落sofa對出地面</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打"},{"pid":"1e2bbb9bad103dc80dca25763e6a6e13d57d741f","tid":163723,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"到佢出黎先再同佢沖涼果啲<br />\n呢家比佢熟悉下環境先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caf42aed5f874efebf4b8f14e15095120fb7e38","tid":163723,"uid":53544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"求其拎一條繩 fing下 就會出黎架喇<br />\n我隻貓就係咁"},{"pid":"6af1a558e2de3d48671f5ae6d331a21483726e9c","tid":163723,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求其拎一條繩 fing下 就會出黎架喇<br />\n我隻貓就係咁</blockquote><br />\n同陌生人太近距離唔一定出"},{"pid":"96cd681e531d16cb3fefbecf893db171fe0cfbf1","tid":163723,"uid":5011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"搵啲好味野食引下佢，佢咁驚應該困下籠，用布包住個籠。<br />\n唔好咁快打針啊，最好住番兩星期左右觀察下無痛無痛先打啦"},{"pid":"9e979c232ebbfb25cc8996b484a3700027193682","tid":163723,"uid":43651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:53:01.000Z","msg":"我隻貓岩岩黎就匿入床下底 捉佢出黎又係走入去<br />\n俾d時間佢 佢至少幾個鐘先出黎 <br />\n準備好野食 水同貓沙 慢慢黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a7e3bb162094fd2cf71c3730f9dd17f08669de","tid":163723,"uid":80629,"like":0,"disl